<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index up Slightly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, November 1 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1,566.63 points on Sunday, up
0.12 points from that of Saturday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,071,205 shares exchanged hands in 1,070 turns and
the turnover stood at 3.94 billion rials (about 657,000
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 27 companies made gains while those of 21 others
declined. 
