<TEXT>
<P>
RAMALLAH, WEST BANK, November 2 (Xinhua) -- Palestinian
National Authority (PNA) and the World Bank signed an agreement on
Monday on the bank's providing 25 million U.S. dollars to support
the Bethlehem 2000 projects.
</P>
<P>
