to PNA Joseph Saba and PNA Finance Minister Mohamad Zuhdi
Nashashibi. PNA President Yasser Arafat was present at the signing
ceremony.
</P>
<P>
Bethlehem, another West Bank town, was the birthplace of Jesus
and the PNA plans to organize various cultural activities in
Bethlehem in the year 2000.
</P>
<P>
