cultural base of the Bethlehem area and foster its sustainable
development through preserving cultural assets and developing
tourism, production and infrastructure in Bethlehem and other
areas of Palestine.
</P>
<P>
The Bethlehem 2000 Authority, Bethlehem Municipality and PNA's
Ministry of Tourism, the Ministry of Culture and the Ministry of
Local Government will be the partners of the projects. 
