<HEADLINE> Romania's PM Visits France </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, November 2 (Xinhua) -- Romania's Prime Minister Radu
Vasile left on Monday morning for France to pay an official
three-day visit to boost traditional cooperation between Bucharest
and Paris.
</P>
<P>
He will meet French President Jacques Chirac, Prime Minister
Lionel Jospin and the speakers of the French parliament.
</P>
<P>
The Romanian prime minister will also meet with representatives
