third in the total volume of commercial exchanges with Romania.
</P>
<P>
France ranked first during the same period in foreign
investment in Romania with about 427 million U.S dollars and 1,757
joint ventures.
</P>
<P>
Paris supports Bucharest in its bid to integrate into the North
Atlantic Treaty Organization and the European Union. 
