<HEADLINE> Guangdong Extends Insured Loans for Car Buyers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, November 2 (Xinhua) -- A local bank and an insurance
company in Guangdong Province have jointly introduced insured
loans for car buyers in a bid to prod the automobile
market.
</P>
<P>
Under this new procedure, potential car buyers are obliged to
buy a loan repayment commitment insurance policy from the
Guangzhou Branch of the China Pacific Insurance Company as a
mortgage applied to car-buying loans from the Guangdong Branch of
the Agriculture Bank of China.
</P>
<P>
