a purchase by installment offered by a local car dealer, local
source said.
</P>
<P>
A survey shows that as many as 26.8 percent of the residents of
Guangzhou, capital of Guangdong Province, want to purchase cars by
the installment plan, making the car-buying market second only to
the housing market in the province. 
