Health and Family Affairs took up various programs to mark the
day.
</P>
<P>
Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina, in her message issued on the eve
of the day, called upon different national, international and
non-government organizations and people from all walks of life to
participate in the programs of voluntary donation of blood and
eye.
</P>
<P>
The government was pledge-bound to take necessary steps for
overcoming the problems of blindness, she stated.
</P>
<P>
The program organizers called to make public aware of the
necessity of donation of blood and posthumous donation of eye.
</P>
<P>
The National Eye Donation Society of Bangladesh has collected
over 1,000 corneas and got eye donation commitment from nearly
30,000 persons in the past ten years since it was established in
1978, according to the official statistics. 
