postgraduate studies in the United Kingdom got the awards from the
scholarship fund set up by the British government in May to assist
students from Malaysia, Indonesia, South Korea and Thailand who
were unable to continue their studies because of the economic
crisis at home, according to the leading national daily.
</P>
<P>
