<HEADLINE> Thai, Myanmar to Develop Border Towns as Tourism Spots </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, November 2 (Xinhua) -- Thai and Myanmar authorities
plan to join hands to develop border towns as tourism spots.
</P>
<P>
